@node "SupportFiles"

    @{b}
    Required Files
    --------------
    @{ub}
    "loadtiga" and the "a2410.device" (latest Version is v1.9)
    are required to get the A2410 going. It should be available
    for A2410 owner. It was part of the Orlando DevCon disks.
    If you do not have it, send me an e-mail. I think we
    can solve this problem.

@endnode
